casebody.data:
Elizabeth PAZOS, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Raudel CRUZ, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 3D18-1800 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 6, 2018 SUAREZ, FERNANDEZ and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Upon consideration, petitioner's motion to stay trial court proceedings is hereby denied.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
